snippet.title: Let's Play The Dragon's Turnabout! [BLIND] Part 1: Previously, On Dual Destinies...
snippet.description:
A DWaM game, taking place after Dual Destinies! [the bad end] 

This was recorded while I was trying to get used to my new headset, so the audio should improve as it goes on!
